Planned meals mean fewer impulse buys. Don’t shop when you are hungry or you will do the same. Shop at the end of the day as you will find the reduced section fully stocked, which means great bargains. Supermarket own-brands can be better and cheaper than named brands. Remember to look for the products with the longest sell-by dates too - you can often find them by rummaging around.
